{
  "chapter": "121",
  "title": "儒林列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我读<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">功令</span>，读到朝廷广泛鼓励<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">学官</span>选拔之路的部分，未尝不放下书本而叹息。我说：唉！<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周室</span>衰落，于是<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">关雎</span>这样的诗篇产生；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周幽王\">幽（周幽王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周厉王\">厉（周厉王）</span>王室衰微，于是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>崩坏；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>各自恣意妄为，政令由强国说了算。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>悯伤王道败废、邪道兴起，就整理编次<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span><span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>，重振<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>。他到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国听了<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">韶</span>乐，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三月（时长）</span>尝不出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>的滋味。从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>返回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>后，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">乐</span>才得以归于正统，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">雅颂</span>各得其所。当时世道混浊，没有人能任用他，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孔子\">仲尼（孔子）</span>奔走干谒了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀</span>位国君而始终不得志，他说：\"如果有能用我的人，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">期月（时长）</span>就可见成效了。\"西郊狩猎捕获<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">麟</span>时，他说：\"我的道走到尽头了。\"于是依据<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">史记</span>作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>，以作为王者之法，文辞含蓄而意旨广博，后世学者多传录它。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "自从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>去世之后，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十子</span>的门徒散游于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间，大者做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">师傅</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卿相</span>，小者与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士大夫</span>为友以教之，或隐居不出。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子路</span>住在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子张</span>住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">澹台子羽</span>住在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夏</span>住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子贡</span>终老于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。像<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田子方</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">段干木</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禽滑釐</span>之类，都曾受业于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夏</span>等人，做过王者之师。这个时候，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏文侯</span>好学。此后儒学日渐衰落，一直到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>时代，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>陷入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">战国</span>相争的局面，儒术被废弃不用；然而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">齐鲁</span>之间，治学者从未间断。在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威（齐威王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣（齐宣王）</span>之际，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀卿</span>一辈，都遵循<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孔子\">夫子（孔子）</span>的学业并加以润色发挥，凭学问显名于当世。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝末世，焚烧<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span><span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>，坑埋<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">术士</span>，\"六艺\"从此残缺。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>称王的时候，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地的诸位儒生抱着<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">孔氏</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼器</span>前去归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">陈王（陈胜）</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span>做了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>，最终与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈涉\">涉（陈涉）</span>一同赴死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>以匹夫身份起事，驱使一群临时纠集的谪戍之卒，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">旬月（时长）</span>之间就在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地称王，不到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">半年（时长）</span>便灭亡，他的作为非常粗浅；然而缙绅先生之流却抱着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼器</span>前去委身称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，为什么呢？因为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>焚烧了他们的学业，他们积怨已久，就把愤怒发泄在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">陈王（陈胜）</span>身上。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高皇帝（刘邦）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span></span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，举兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span></span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地的诸儒还在讲诵习练<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>，弦歌之声不绝。这难道不是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣人</span>遗留的教化、一个好<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>的国度吗？所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>时说：\"回去吧，回去吧！我乡党的小子们志向高远而行事率略，文采斐然自成章法，却不知如何剪裁节制。\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">齐鲁</span>之间重视<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>，自古以来就是这样，是他们的天性。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起，诸儒才得以修习他们的经典，讲习<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">大射乡饮之礼</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>制定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼仪</span>，因此升任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>，那些共同参与制礼的诸生<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>，也都在选拔中居于前列，于是大家慨然感叹，兴起向学之风。然而当时还有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">干戈</span>未息，忙于平定四海，也无暇顾及学校之事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉惠帝\">孝惠（汉惠帝）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>都是靠武力建功的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文（汉文帝）</span>时稍有征用，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文帝（汉文帝）</span>本性喜好<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">刑名</span>之学。到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>，不任用儒者，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>又喜好<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">黄老之术</span>，所以诸<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>只是备员等待咨询，没有得到升进的。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">今上（汉武帝）</span>即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵绾</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王臧</span>之类通晓儒学，皇上也倾向儒学，于是招揽<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">方正贤良文学</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。 从此以后，讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>者，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>就推<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申培公</span>，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>就推<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕固生</span>，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>就推<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩婴\">韩太傅（韩婴）</span>。 讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济南</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>始。 讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高堂生</span>始。 讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">菑川</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田何\">田生（田何）</span>始。 讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">齐鲁</span>自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡毋生</span>始，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>始。 到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>后，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武安侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田蚡</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，罢黜<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">黄老</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">刑名</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">百家</span>之言，延聘<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>儒者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百人</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>凭<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>从布衣升为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平津侯</span>。 <span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的学<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>都一齐向儒学归风。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">学官</span>，痛惜儒道被壅塞，于是上请说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>奏说：陛下下制书说'听说引导<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众要用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>，教化他们要用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">乐</span>。婚姻是居家之大伦。如今<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>废<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">乐</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，朕十分忧虑。因此广招<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">方正博闻</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，使他们都登上朝廷。命令<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼官</span>劝勉学业，讲议广博见闻以振兴<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>，以此为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>作表率。让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>及<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>议定办法，弘扬乡里的教化，广泛选拔贤才'。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "我们谨与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太常臧\">臧（太常臧）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：博士平\">平（博士平）</span>等人商议说：听说<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>之道，乡里有学校，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>叫<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">校</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>叫<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">序</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>叫<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">庠</span>。其劝善的办法是在朝廷上褒扬；其惩恶的办法是施加<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">刑罚</span>。所以推行教化，首要的善举从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>开始，由内而外。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>昭示至德，开启大明，与<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">天地</span>相配，本于人伦，劝勉学业，修明<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>乐，崇教化、励贤才，以此教化四方，这是太平的本源。古时政教未备，礼制未全，我们请求凭借旧官兴办。为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>官配置<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十人</span>，免除他们的徭役。让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>选择年龄<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十八已上</span>、仪容端正的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>，补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>。郡国县道邑有好<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>、尊敬长上、肃敬政教、顺善乡里、出入言行不悖所闻的人，让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞</span>上报所属<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>谨慎察考合格者，随同上计者一起送到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>，让他们与<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>同受学业。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>后都进行考试，通晓一经以上的，补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文学</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掌故</span>的缺员；其中成绩优异可任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>的，由<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>登录上奏。如有特别优异的秀才，立即上报其姓名。那些不事学业或资质低下、不能通晓一经的，就罢免之；并对所举荐不称职者加以处罚。我们谨依所下达的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">诏书律令</span>，明辨<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天人</span>的分际，贯通古今的义理，文章<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">尔雅</span>，训辞深厚，恩泽极美。小吏见闻浅薄，不能完全阐发，无法明白晓谕下面。治<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>次为治<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掌故</span>，以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>为官，迁升滞缓。请挑选其中俸秩比<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二百石</span>以上者，以及吏员中俸禄<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百石</span>而通一经以上的，补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左右内史</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行卒史</span>；秩比<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百石</span>以下的，补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郡太守卒史</span>：每处各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，边郡<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。优先用诵习经文较多的；如果人数不足，就选<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掌故</span>补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中二千石</span>的属官，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文学</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掌故</span>补为郡属官，以备员额。请把这些写入<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">功令</span>。其余照<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律令</span>办理。\"制书批答：\"可以。\"从此以来，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿大夫</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>吏之中，文质彬彬、多有<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>了。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高祖（刘邦）</span>经过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>身份跟从老师到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鲁南宫</span>觐见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高祖（刘邦）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕太后（吕雉）</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>游学，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘郢</span>同师。后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘郢\">郢（刘郢）</span>做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>做他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘戊\">戊（刘戊）</span>的师傅。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘戊\">戊（刘戊）</span>不好学，憎恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>。等到王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘郢\">郢（刘郢）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">卒</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘戊\">戊（刘戊）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>罚作刑徒。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>以此为耻，回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国，退居家中教授，终身不出家门，也谢绝<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>，唯独王有命召见才去。从远方来受业的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>只以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">诗经</span>作为训解来教授，没有写成传文；遇到疑难处就存疑不传。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">兰陵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王臧</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>处受了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>以后，以此事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景帝（汉景帝）</span>做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子少傅</span>，后被免职离去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">今上（汉武帝）</span>初即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王臧\">臧（王臧）</span>就上书请求做皇上的宿卫，累经升迁，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>之中做到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中令</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵绾</span>也曾在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>处受<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵绾\">绾（赵绾）</span>做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵绾\">绾（赵绾）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王臧\">臧（王臧）</span>请<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，想建立<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">明堂</span>以朝见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，但办不成此事，就推荐他们的老师<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派使者，备<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">束帛</span>加<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">璧</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">安车</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">驷马</span>迎请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">轺传</span>跟从。到京后，朝见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>问<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">治乱</span>之事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>当时已<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八十馀</span>岁，年老，回答说：\"治理国家不在于多说，只看力行怎么样罢了。\" 当时<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>正喜好华丽文辞，见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>如此对答，默然无语。不过既已召来，就让他做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span>，住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鲁邸</span>，商议<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">明堂</span>之事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太皇窦太后</span>喜好<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">老子</span>之言，不喜欢<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒术</span>，抓住<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵绾</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王臧</span>的过失责让皇上，皇上因此废置<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">明堂</span>之事，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵绾</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王臧</span>全部交付司法，后来两人都自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span></span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>也称病免官归乡，几年后去世。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "他的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔安国</span>官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">临淮太守</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周霸</span>至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">胶西内史</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏宽</span>至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">城阳内史</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀鲁</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁赐\">赐（鲁赐）</span>至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东海太守</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">兰陵</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪生</span>至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长沙内史</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐偃</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">胶西中尉</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邹</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阙门庆忌</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">胶东内史</span>。他们治理官<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>都有廉洁的节操，称得上好学。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">学官</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>中，德行虽有不备之处，但做到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掌故</span>的以百计。讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>的虽有不同，但大多本于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">清河王太傅</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕固生</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人。因治<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>时做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>。他与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄生</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">景帝（汉景帝）</span>面前争论。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄生</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>不是受天命，乃是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>君。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕固生</span>说：\"不对。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>暴虐混乱，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>人心都归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>顺应<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的人心而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span></span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>都不为他们所用而归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>不得已才即位，这不是受命又是什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄生</span>说：\"<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠</span>虽破，必定戴在头上；<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">履</span>虽新，必定穿在脚上。为什么呢？是上下的分别。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>虽然失道，毕竟还是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>上；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>虽然圣明，毕竟还是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>下。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主有过失的行为，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>下不能直言匡正其过而使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>受<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">尊</span>崇，反而借他的过错而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span></span>杀他，取代他南面为王，这不是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>君是什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕固生</span>说：\"照你所说，那<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>取代<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>即<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之位，也不对吗？\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">景帝（汉景帝）</span>说：\"吃<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>不吃<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">马肝</span>，不能算不知<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>味；讲学者不谈<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>受命的事，不能算愚笨。\" 便停止了争论。此后，学者没有人敢公开谈论受命放<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span></span>之事了。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>喜爱<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">老子</span>书，召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕固生</span>来问<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">老子</span>这部书。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>说：\"这不过是下人之言罢了。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>发怒说：\"哪里比得上<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司空</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">城旦</span>的刑书呢？\" 就让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">圈</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span></span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">豕</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">景帝（汉景帝）</span>知道<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>发怒而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>直言无罪，就借给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>锋利的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>器，让他下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">圈</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span></span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">豕</span>，正中<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">豕</span>的心脏，一<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span></span>，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">豕</span>就应手倒下。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>默然无语，找不到别的理由加罪，就让他出来了。过不久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">景帝（汉景帝）</span>认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>廉洁正直，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">清河王太傅</span>。过了很久，因病免职。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">今上（汉武帝）</span>初即位，又以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">贤良</span>的名义征召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>。那些阿谀之儒多憎恨诋毁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>，说\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>老了\"，就罢免遣归。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>已<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九十馀</span>岁。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>被征召时，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>也被征召，侧目而视<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>对他说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙子</span>，务必以正学立言，不要曲学迎合世俗！\" 从此以后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>的都以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕固生</span>为宗。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人中凭<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>显贵的，都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：辕固生\">固（辕固生）</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩生</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文帝（汉文帝）</span>时做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">景帝（汉景帝）</span>时做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">常山王太傅</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩生</span>推演<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>的意旨作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">内外传</span>共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万言</span>，他的说法颇与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">齐鲁</span>之间不同，但归旨一致。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮南</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贲生</span>从他受业。从此以后，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">燕赵</span>之间讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>的都源自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩生</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩生</span>的孙子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩商\">商（韩商）</span>做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">今上（汉武帝）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济南</span>人。原是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文帝（汉文帝）</span>时，想寻求能治<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>的人，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>没有，才听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>能治，想征召他。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>年九十多岁，年老不能行走，于是就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">诏</span>令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掌故</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晁错</span>前去受学。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝焚书时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>把书藏在墙壁中。后来战事大起，他流亡在外，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝平定后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>找回他的书，丢失了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十篇</span>，只剩下<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十九篇</span>，就用来在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">齐鲁</span>之间教授。学者们由此相当能讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>了，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大师</span>没有不涉及<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>来教授的。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>教<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济南</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张生</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">欧阳生</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">欧阳生</span>教<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">千乘</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒宽</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒宽</span>既通晓<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>，又以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>应郡里举荐，到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>门下受业，跟从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔安国</span>学习。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒宽</span>贫穷没有费用，常为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>们做炊事，时时还抽空出去做雇工，以供衣食。路上常带着经书，停下休息时就诵习它。经考试列出名次后，补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉史</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张汤</span>正倾向儒学，就任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒宽</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">奏谳掾</span>，用古代的法意断决疑难大案，很宠爱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：兒宽\">宽（兒宽）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：兒宽\">宽（兒宽）</span>为人温良，廉洁明智，能克制自己，擅长撰文写奏章，下笔敏捷，但口才不佳。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>认为他是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>，多次称赞他。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒宽</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掾</span>，把他推荐给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>召见询问，很喜欢他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张汤</span>死后六年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒宽</span>位至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。做了九年官而在任上去世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：兒宽\">宽（兒宽）</span>身居<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>之位，凭温和善良顺承上意以得长久，但从没有什么匡正规谏；在官时，属吏轻视他，不肯尽力。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张生</span>也做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伏生</span>的孙子以治<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>被征召，却不能阐明其义。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "自此以后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周霸</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔安国</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贾嘉</span>，颇能讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>之事。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">孔氏</span>家有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">古文尚书</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孔安国\">安国（孔安国）</span>以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">今文</span>读之，因此而立起他的家学。得到<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">逸书</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀篇</span>，大约<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>由此而益发丰富。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "诸学者多讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高堂生</span>最合根本。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>原本自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>时经典就不完备，到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>焚书时，散失更多，如今只剩<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">士礼</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高堂生</span>能讲它。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐生</span>擅长<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">容</span>礼。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文帝（汉文帝）</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐生</span>以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">容</span>礼做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">礼官大夫</span>。传给儿子，再传给孙子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：徐延\">延（徐延）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐襄</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：徐襄\">襄（徐襄）</span>天资擅长<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">容</span>礼，却不能通<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼经</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：徐延\">延（徐延）</span>还颇能通，但不擅长<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">容</span>礼。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：徐襄\">襄（徐襄）</span>以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">容</span>礼任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">礼官大夫</span>，官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">广陵内史</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：徐延\">延（徐延）</span>以及<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">徐氏</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公户满意</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓生</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">单次</span>，都曾做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">礼官大夫</span>。而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瑕丘</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧奋</span>以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阳太守</span>。此后能讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>、能行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">容</span>礼的，都源于<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">徐氏</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "自从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商瞿</span>从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>受<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">卒</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商瞿</span>传<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>，经<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六世（时长）</span>传到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田何</span>，字<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田何\">子庄（田何）</span>，此时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田何</span>传给<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东武</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王同</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王同\">子仲（王同）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王同\">子仲（王同）</span>传给<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">菑川</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨何</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杨何\">何（杨何）</span>因<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元光元年</span>被征召，官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：即墨成\">成（即墨成）</span>以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">城阳相</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广川</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟但</span>以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子门大夫</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周霸</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">衡胡</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临菑</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主父偃</span>，都凭<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>。但讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>的大都本于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨何</span>之家。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广川</span>人。因治<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>时做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>。他放下帷幕讲诵，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>们按入门先后相传受业，有人甚至见不到他的面，大概<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>之间<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>都没到园中一望，他专精到如此地步。他的进退容止，不合<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>就不做，学<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>都以师礼尊奉他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">今上（汉武帝）</span>即位，任他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">江都相</span>。他以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>所记灾异之变来推论<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">阴阳</span>所以错行的原因，所以求雨就关闭阳类，放纵阴类；止雨就反过来做。在一国之内施行，从未有求而不得的。中间被贬为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span>，闲居家中，撰著<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">灾异之记</span>。当时<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">高庙</span>发生火灾，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主父偃</span>嫉恨他，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span></span>了他的书稿奏上<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>召来诸生给他们看此书，认为其中有<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\"><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span></span>讥之语。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕步舒</span>不知道这是他师父的书，斥为下愚之作。于是把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>交付有司，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当死</span>罪，诏令<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span>免了他。从此<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>再也不敢讲灾异。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>为人廉洁正直。当时朝廷正向外攘斥<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">四夷</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>治<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙弘\">弘（公孙弘）</span>善于迎合世俗而得用事，位至<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙弘\">弘（公孙弘）</span>阿谀从众。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙弘\">弘（公孙弘）</span>憎恨他，就对皇上说：\"只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>可以去做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：胶西缪王刘端\">缪西王（胶西缪王刘端）</span>的相。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">胶西王（刘端）</span>素来听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>有德行，也善待他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>担心久后获罪，称病免官居家。直到死，终生不经营产业，只以修学著书为事。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起以来的<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五世（时长）</span>之间，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>以通<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>闻名，他传的是<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">公羊氏</span>之学。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡毋生</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>时做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>，年老回乡教授。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>的多受业于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡毋生</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>也颇受益于他。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瑕丘</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">江生</span>治<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">穀梁春秋</span>。自从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>得到任用，他曾经汇集比较各家义旨，最终采用了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>之学。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：董仲舒\">仲舒（董仲舒）</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>中有成就的：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">兰陵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚大</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广川</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">殷忠</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">温</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕步舒</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚大</span>官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕步舒\">步舒（吕步舒）</span>官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长史</span>，持节出使裁决<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮南</span>谋反的案件，对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>擅自专断不奏报，就以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>之义来裁正，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>都认为他做得对。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>中学问通达的，做到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">命大夫</span>者；做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掌故</span>者以百计。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>的儿子和孙子都凭学问做到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大官</span>。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">孔氏</span>之学衰微，经书线索纷乱。 讲六学，始于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">炎汉</span>。 著为法令、设立<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">学官</span>，四方响应。 曲台坏壁之间，书<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>为首。 传<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>讲<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>，云蒸雾散。 兴教化、致治理，宏大谋略<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">克</span>成。"
    }
  }
}